Name: Max Moon
Desc: She is in good shape and has healthy skin colour.A big rockets logo in her T-shirt.

Name: Marry Sue
Desc: A big pair of glasses cover nearly a half of her face, her hair looks like a rainbow and decorated with some colourful little stars.

Name: Jessica
Desc: She has a cross tottoo in her forehead wears in a Gothic style. A "Hell Kitchen" T-shirt probably means she serves in catering services.

Name: Daro.The Retailer
Desc: She drives a ice cream van which brand you like best.She ties her hair a ponytail style and wear the ice-cream uniform.

Name: Princess Anduin Mrynn
Desc: She wears a white sliver arour looks like a knight,but I can see some dark gas surrounding her.When you move near her, you feel very very cold.
Brief_Desc: an princess looking like a priest

Name: Lady Mamba
Desc: Her hair is ten living snakes.She wears a big sunglasses and hold a mirror ,repeating that who is the most beautiful women in the world.

Name: Princess Beauty
Desc: She wears heavy makeup and is stronger and taller than everyone you have ever met.

Name: Cleopatra VII
Desc: She is so shining and the golden jewelrys are so shining too. You nearly can not open your eyes becuase of the lights.

Name: Lady Merlin
Desc: She wears a dark grey cloak and hides her face in the shadow,what you can see are just her green eyes.

Name: Gabrielle
Desc: You hate feathers! She may be beautiful but the 12 wings in her back makes her like a fat bied what you can see are only ferthers!feathers! And feathers!"Astishoo!!!!"

Name: Belial.The ArchDemon
Desc: The most obese and greasiest Evil you have never see. He is sitting there chewing something.You guess he can not see his own feet .The wings are so tiny compared to his shape, you wonder whether he can fly…

Name: Belial.The Coolest Demon
Desc: He is so handsome and looks like the Mr. right in fairy tales.You can only  recognize his demon identity by the devil horns. Maybe you could fall in love with him if you were a girl.

Name: J.Harden
Desc: He is very strong, and in red sportswear, flourishing whiskers cover his chin.

Name: Lady of Lake
Desc: She completely looks like Merlin,althoug you do not know what Merlin really looks like.The only different thing is the coulour of cloak,hers is white.

Name: Athena
Desc: She is a plaster model and she keeps talking something.You feel like a noisy bumming bee flying around your ears.

Name: Gullow
Desc: His eyes are very big  which nearly takers over his whole face."My precious.My precious!"he repeats and looks for something.

Name: Mr Oldman
Desc: A weird old man with long long long goatee.You gusses he konw everything in the world.

Name: Lost soul
Desc: A lost soul whose death is obviously related to demons years or centuries ago. Haunting around the mansion of devils.
